Jonathan Dickson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jonathan_Dickson 0 Jonathan Macgregor Dickson (born July 26, 1974) is an American actor. He is best known for his role as Professor Blackjack (Edward O. Thorp) on the History Channel's Breaking Vegas series. He has also appeared in such shows as 30 ROCK and Boardwalk Empire. He can be seen shag dancing next to Rachel McAdams and James Marsden in the romantic drama, The Notebook. Jonathan_Macgregor_Dickson ( born July_26_,_1974 ) is an_American_actor .
